#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.95"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.95:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.95:0.2"
msgid "10. Loṇakapallavagga"
msgstr "10. A Lump of Salt"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.95:0.3"
msgid "95. Parisāsutta"
msgstr "95. Assemblies"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.95:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, parisā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these are the three assemblies."

msgctxt "an3.95:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.95:1.3"
msgid "Aggavatī parisā, vaggā parisā, samaggā parisā."
msgstr "An assembly of the best, a divided assembly, and a harmonious assembly."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.243"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.95:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, aggavatī parisā?"
msgstr "And what is an assembly of the best?"

msgctxt "an3.95:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, yassaṃ parisāyaṃ therā bhikkhū na bāhulikā honti na "
"sāthalikā, okkamane nikkhittadhurā paviveke pubbaṅgamā, vīriyaṃ ārabhanti "
"appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya, "
"tesaṃ pacchimā janatā diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"An assembly where the senior mendicants are not indulgent or slack, nor are "
"they backsliders. Instead, they take the lead in seclusion, rousing energy "
"for attaining the unattained, achieving the unachieved, and realizing the "
"unrealized. And those who come afterwards follow their example."

msgctxt "an3.95:2.3"
msgid ""
"Sāpi hoti na bāhulikā na sāthalikā okkamane nikkhittadhurā paviveke "
"pubbaṅgamā, vīriyaṃ ārabhati appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya "
"asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya."
msgstr ""
"They too are not indulgent or slack, nor are they backsliders. Instead, they "
"take the lead in seclusion, rousing energy for attaining the unattained, "
"achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized."

msgctxt "an3.95:2.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, aggavatī parisā."
msgstr "This is called an assembly of the best."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.95:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, vaggā parisā?"
msgstr "And what is a divided assembly?"

msgctxt "an3.95:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, yassaṃ parisāyaṃ bhikkhū bhaṇḍanajātā kalahajātā "
"vivādāpannā aññamaññaṃ mukhasattīhi vitudantā viharanti, ayaṃ vuccati, "
"bhikkhave, vaggā parisā."
msgstr ""
"An assembly where the mendicants argue, quarrel, and fight, continually "
"wounding each other with barbed words. This is called a divided assembly."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.95:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, samaggā parisā?"
msgstr "And what is a harmonious assembly?"

msgctxt "an3.95:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, yassaṃ parisāyaṃ bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā "
"khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, ayaṃ vuccati, "
"bhikkhave, samaggā parisā."
msgstr ""
"An assembly where the mendicants live in harmony, appreciating each other, "
"without quarreling, blending like milk and water, and regarding each other "
"with kindly eyes. This is called a harmonious assembly."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.95:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, bhikkhave, samaye bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā "
"khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, bahuṃ, "
"bhikkhave, bhikkhū tasmiṃ samaye puññaṃ pasavanti."
msgstr "When the mendicants live in harmony like this, they make much merit."

msgctxt "an3.95:5.2"
msgid ""
"Brahmaṃ, bhikkhave, vihāraṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhū viharanti, yadidaṃ "
"muditāya cetovimuttiyā."
msgstr ""
"At that time the mendicants live in a holy dwelling, that is, the heart’s "
"release by rejoicing."

msgctxt "an3.95:5.3"
msgid ""
"Pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ "
"vediyati, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""
"When you’re joyful, rapture springs up. When the mind is full of rapture, "
"the body becomes tranquil. When the body is tranquil, you feel bliss. And "
"when you’re blissful, the mind becomes immersed in samādhi."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: kusobbhe → kussubbhe (bj, pts1) | kussobbhe (s1-3, km, mr)
#. VAR: samuddaṃ → samuddasāgare (mr)
msgctxt "an3.95:6.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, uparipabbate thullaphusitake deve vassante taṃ udakaṃ "
"yathāninnaṃ pavattamānaṃ pabbatakandarapadarasākhā paripūreti, "
"pabbatakandarapadarasākhā paripūrā kusobbhe paripūrenti, kusobbhā paripūrā "
"mahāsobbhe paripūrenti, mahāsobbhā paripūrā kunnadiyo paripūrenti, kunnadiyo "
"paripūrā mahānadiyo paripūrenti, mahānadiyo paripūrā samuddaṃ paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"It’s like when it rains heavily on a mountain top, and the water flows "
"downhill to fill the hollows, crevices, and creeks. As they become full, "
"they fill up the pools. The pools fill up the lakes, the lakes fill up the "
"streams, and the streams fill up the rivers. And as the rivers become full, "
"they fill up the ocean."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.244"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an3.95:7.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ samaye bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā "
"avivadamānā khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, "
"bahuṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū tasmiṃ samaye puññaṃ pasavanti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, when the mendicants are in harmony, appreciating each "
"other, without quarreling, blending like milk and water, and regarding each "
"other with kindly eyes, they make much merit."

msgctxt "an3.95:7.2"
msgid ""
"Brahmaṃ, bhikkhave, vihāraṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhū viharanti, yadidaṃ "
"muditāya cetovimuttiyā."
msgstr ""
"At that time the mendicants live in a holy dwelling, that is, the heart’s "
"release by rejoicing."

msgctxt "an3.95:7.3"
msgid ""
"Pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ "
"vediyati, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""
"When you’re joyful, rapture springs up. When the mind is full of rapture, "
"the body becomes tranquil. When the body is tranquil, you feel bliss. And "
"when you’re blissful, the mind becomes immersed in samādhi."

msgctxt "an3.95:7.4"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso parisā”ti."
msgstr "These are the three assemblies.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.95:7.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
